1
00:00:00,542 --> 00:00:04,143
拿撒勒人散播谣言说
The Nazarene spread rumor that he would rise

2
00:00:04,145 --> 00:00:06,412
他会在死去三天后复生
from his own death after three days.

3
00:00:06,414 --> 00:00:09,047
让神殿的护卫把守在外面
Post temple guards outside.

4
00:00:09,049 --> 00:00:11,518
而我会派遣罗马士兵
And I will post Roman soldiers.

5
00:00:17,957 --> 00:00:19,458
- 我看到他了  - 谁?
- I saw him.  - Who?

6
00:00:19,460 --> 00:00:20,926
耶稣
Jesus.

7
00:00:20,928 --> 00:00:22,795
你相信他已经死而复生了吗?
Do you believe he has risen from the dead?

8
00:00:22,797 --> 00:00:24,697
他曾保证这些都会发生
It's what he promised would happen.

9
00:00:24,699 --> 00:00:27,466
是时候由我们来结束这个故事了
It's time we shut this story down.

10
00:00:27,468 --> 00:00:29,435
杀掉所有坟墓守卫
Kill all the tomb guards.

11
00:00:31,138 --> 00:00:33,838
罗马皇帝的封印已经被破坏了
The Emperor's seal is broken.

12
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:35,206
我们究竟是走还是留?
Do we stay or go?

13
00:00:35,208 --> 00:00:37,442
我让我的朋友们去城门口集合
I told my friends to make their way to the city gate

14
00:00:37,444 --> 00:00:40,644
- 然后想办法找到一条路  - 我们可以帮忙
- so we can find a way out.  - We can help.

15
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,681
- 现在就走  - 你为什么帮助我们?
- Go now.  - Why are you helping us?

16
00:00:43,683 --> 00:00:44,949
罗马人的敌人就是我们的朋友
An enemy of theirs is a friend of ours.

17
00:00:44,951 --> 00:00:46,917
是看守拿撒勒人坟墓的祭司们
The priests guarding the Nazarene's tomb.

18
00:00:46,919 --> 00:00:48,586
他们怎么了?
What of them?

19
00:00:48,588 --> 00:00:51,621
其中两位发现被人谋杀 而其余的都失踪了
Two of them found murdered, and the others are missing.

20
00:00:51,623 --> 00:00:53,490
回到耶路撒冷等待即可
Go back to Jerusalem and wait.

21
00:00:53,492 --> 00:00:59,195
圣灵降临在你们身上 你们就必得着能力
And the power of the holy spirit will come to you.

