Give us today our daily bread, and forgive us our debts...

400
00:29:38,469 --> 00:29:44,408
现在我们要离开此地
Now we can leave this place.

401
00:29:44,410 --> 00:29:48,111
现在我们为他传道
Now we spread his word.

402
00:29:58,822 --> 00:30:01,090
不论如何 我们都要保护巡抚!
At all times, we shield the governor!

403
00:30:01,092 --> 00:30:03,492
谁若敢上前一步...
The first person to step forward...

404
00:30:03,494 --> 00:30:04,827
我就取他的首级
I'll have his head.

405
00:30:22,011 --> 00:30:25,680
巡抚 大祭司要您跟着我
Governor, the high priest would ask that you follow me

406
00:30:25,682 --> 00:30:27,415
从神殿的南门进去
and enter the temple through one of the south gates.

407
00:30:27,417 --> 00:30:29,783
为什么?
Why?

408
00:30:29,785 --> 00:30:31,151
那扇美门通往妇人院
The Beautiful Gate leads to the Court of the Women,

409
00:30:31,153 --> 00:30:32,953
只有犹太人才能进入
which is for Jews only.

410
00:30:32,955 --> 00:30:37,291
他还礼貌地要求您把武器留在外面
He also requests politely that you leave your weapons outside.

411
00:30:37,293 --> 00:30:39,793
那我礼貌地拒绝这两条要求
I decline both requests politely.

412
00:30:39,795 --> 00:30:41,695
我们就从这里进去
We enter here.

413
00:30:41,697 --> 00:30:42,963
列队!
Cohort!

414
00:31:51,694 --> 00:31:52,695
我们去哪?
Where are we going?

415
00:31:52,697 --> 00:31:54,563
神殿啊 还能去哪?
The temple. Where else?

416
00:31:59,303 --> 00:32:02,737
我希望你清楚自己在做什么 该亚法
I do hope you know what you're doing, Caiaphas.

417
00:32:02,739 --> 00:32:04,706
你真的以为这样能行?
And you really believe this will work?

418
00:32:04,708 --> 00:32:07,776
如果不成功 他们会同罗马人一起撕了我们
If it doesn't, they'll tear us apart along with the Romans.

419
00:32:20,189 --> 00:32:22,790
请肃静!
Quiet, please!

420
00:32:22,792 --> 00:32:25,560
肃静
Quiet.

421
00:32:26,692 --> 00:32:29,460
请大家肃静

422
00:32:30,992 --> 00:32:35,160
我知道以前从未有巡抚光临

423
00:32:36,092 --> 00:32:38,560
但你们要明白

424
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:42,641
他来此是为赎自己的罪

425
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,641
他在说什么?
What's he saying?

426
00:32:43,740 --> 00:32:47,741
他带了礼物向我们的信仰致敬

427
00:32:48,140 --> 00:32:52,741
并要在神前屈身敬拜

428
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:56,141
所以与其谴责

429
00:32:56,940 --> 00:32:59,341
我们应当宽容他

430
00:33:39,029 --> 00:33:41,464
右边有情况!
Trouble to the right!

431
00:33:42,832 --> 00:33:43,832
上!
Go!

432
00:33:47,638 --> 00:33:49,405
别挡着路!
Get out of the way!

433
00:33:58,814 --> 00:34:00,014
闪开!
Move!

434
00:34:05,020 --> 00:34:06,020
哥尼流!
Cornelius!

435
00:34:09,192 --> 00:34:09,991
让路!
Make way!

436
00:34:09,993 --> 00:34:11,192
别挡着路!
Get out of my way!

437
00:34:22,237 --> 00:34:23,671
起来
Up.

438
00:34:29,176 --> 00:34:31,043
但愿你死得其所
I hope your cause is worth dying for.

439
00:34:31,045 --> 00:34:32,437
愿你如此
I hope yours is.

440
00:34:50,437 --> 00:34:52,052
给点钱吧 大人?
A few coins, master?

441
00:35:00,628 --> 00:35:02,295
你看我们
Look at us.

442
00:35:02,297 --> 00:35:04,330
我们没钱
We have no money.

443
00:35:06,099 --> 00:35:08,234
金银我都没有
No silver, no gold.

444
00:35:16,175 --> 00:35:23,782
只把我所有的给你 我奉拿撒勒人耶稣的名给你
But what I have I give you in the name of Jesus of Nazareth.

445
00:35:25,052 --> 00:35:28,486
叫你起来行走
Rise up and walk.

446
00:35:53,978 --> 00:35:59,549
藉着耶稣 这人能重新行走了
It's through Jesus that this man walks again.

447
00:35:59,551 --> 00:36:05,220
神给我们差来他的仆人 耶稣
God sent us his servant, Jesus,

448
00:36:05,222 --> 00:36:11,760
神又叫他从死里复活了
and God raised him again from death.

449
00:36:11,762 --> 00:36:14,497
我们是他的见证
We are his witnesses,

450
00:36:14,499 --> 00:36:18,266
圣灵与我们同在 让我们坚强
and the holy spirit is with us and makes us strong.

451
00:36:18,268 --> 00:36:21,402
耶稣还活着
Jesus is alive.

452
00:36:24,073 --> 00:36:26,774
让以色列众人知道...
Let all Israel know...

453
00:36:26,776 --> 00:36:31,779
神立耶稣为主 为弥赛亚了
God made Jesus Lord and Messiah.

454
00:36:32,781 --> 00:36:35,416
我以为你已经摆平这些信众了 该亚法
I thought you had dealt with these followers, Caiaphas.

455
00:36:35,418 --> 00:36:37,384
加入我们
Join us,

456
00:36:37,386 --> 00:36:41,054
你们也必领受圣灵
and you, too, will receive the holy spirit.

457
00:36:41,056 --> 00:36:44,758
让他们闭嘴 以免再起骚乱
Silence them now, before he starts another riot.

458
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:46,793
来吧 拯救你们自己脱离这残酷的...
Come, save yourselves from this cruel wo...

459
00:36:47,963 --> 00:36:49,763
彼得!
Peter!

460
00:36:49,765 --> 00:36:51,264
耶稣已复活
Jesus is risen,

461
00:36:51,266 --> 00:36:53,799
上帝将在天空显出奇事
and God will perform wonders in the sky above

462
00:36:53,801 --> 00:36:56,736
在地上显出神迹!
and miracles in the earth below!

463
00:36:58,540 --> 00:37:03,475
日头要变为黑暗 月亮要变为血!
The sun will turn to darkness and the moon to blood!

464
00:37:51,488 --> 00:37:53,590
有人发现马尔库斯·德鲁苏斯被杀害了
Marcus Drusus was found murdered.

465
00:37:53,592 --> 00:37:56,192
我们在附近逮捕了一伙人
We've arrested a group of men in the immediate area.

466
00:37:56,194 --> 00:37:58,327
处决他们
Execute them.

467
00:37:58,329 --> 00:38:00,862
我们认为凶手不在其中
W... we don't think the killer's among them.

468
00:38:00,864 --> 00:38:07,736
在神殿台阶上处决他们所有人
Execute them all on the steps of the temple.

469
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,207
遵命
As you wish.

470
00:38:33,161 --> 00:38:34,161
彼得
Peter.

471
00:38:36,030 --> 00:38:38,197
- 玛利亚  - 约翰
- Mary.  - John.

472
00:38:38,199 --> 00:38:39,866
其他人都很安全
All the others are safe.

473
00:38:39,868 --> 00:38:40,967
你的伤...
Your wounds...

474
00:38:40,969 --> 00:38:42,268
没什么
They're nothing.

475
00:38:44,739 --> 00:38:46,973
外面的情况怎么样了?
What's happening out there?

476
00:38:46,975 --> 00:38:51,511
他的道如燎原之火 就像圣灵一般
Word has spread like a fire, like the spirit itself.

477
00:38:51,513 --> 00:38:55,614
许多许多人在奔我们而来 或许有数千人之多
Many, many people are coming to us, perhaps thousands.

478
00:38:58,351 --> 00:39:00,953
玛雅
Maya.

479
00:39:04,524 --> 00:39:07,926
她说在你安全回去之前是不会睡的
She says she won't sleep until you're safely back.

480
00:39:07,928 --> 00:39:13,097
玛利亚 请你照顾好她
Mary, please take care of her.

481
00:39:13,099 --> 00:39:14,966
我们可能永远出不去了
We may never leave here.

482
00:39:27,979 --> 00:39:29,713
站起来... 快点
On your feet... Come on.

483
00:39:29,715 --> 00:39:31,882
不! 不 不! 我是无辜的!
No! No, no! I'm innocent!

484
00:40:03,713 --> 00:40:06,380
把杀手交出来
Deliver the assassin to us,

485
00:40:06,382 --> 00:40:09,450
否则眼前这幕将不断重复上演
or this will become an all-too-familiar spectacle.

486
00:40:33,174 --> 00:40:35,942
他们会找你的
They are going to be looking for you.

487
00:40:40,513 --> 00:40:44,350
他们正在外邦人院处死嫌疑人
They're executing suspects at the Court of the Gentiles.

488
00:40:49,656 --> 00:40:53,024
世态如此
It's the way of the world.

489
