Blessed be the name of his glorious kingdom

499
00:41:28,726 --> 00:41:31,838
直到永永远远
forever and ever.

500
00:41:42,026 --> 00:41:44,638
我们的人已经不计其数了
We are already beyond counting.

501
00:41:46,026 --> 00:41:50,638
当他们的信仰席卷整个大地 帝国开始施行报复
As their faith sweeps the land and the Empire retaliates.

502
00:41:50,726 --> 00:41:52,938
杀手是冲我而来
The assassin came for me.

503
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:57,638
每天钉死十个犹太人...
Ten Jews will be crucified every day...

504
00:41:58,326 --> 00:42:00,238
你知道这也不会容易
You knew this wasn't going to be easy.

505
00:42:00,526 --> 00:42:03,138
绝不手下留情
There will be no mercy.

506
00:42:03,426 --> 00:42:05,638
我儿子选择你是有原因的
My son chose you for a reason.
